    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321120/extras/369bdf1adc86d49dd4554f9a4a6dccda.avif?t=1729050857\" width=600 height=252 /></span><br><strong>《纯爱声放送》</strong>是一款以声音导演、广播剧录制为主题的纯爱向剧情游戏。<br>主角亚树拥有通过声音听出说话者真实情绪，发现一切真实与虚假的能力。独自成立了录音工作室，却陷入经营危机，只得以协助友人录制BL广播剧，来缓解财务状况。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【白手起家开始录音】</h2>接取不同类别的广播剧，进行学习与取材。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321120/extras/85746b744cd61b83baedc4d68aeb73ed.avif?t=1729050857\" width=616 height=292 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【每部剧都尽心尽力】</h2>选择你喜欢的配音演员，并全程参与指导。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321120/extras/2d85743b3569a959befbda2fc37a11c0.avif?t=1729050857\" width=616 height=292 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【更加地...了解他们】</h2>周末可以与你感兴趣的他相遇，了解他的故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321120/extras/7c74f47769674ea216703caa0fa14ca7.avif?t=1729050857\" width=616 height=292 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【与他们的纯爱之旅】</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321120/extras/507179d5d02d16b96e809daef1d2675d.avif?t=1729050857\" width=616 height=293 /></span>",
